    <%# join part %>
    <div class="features features-qvm1rmb features-qvm1rmb-join">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="intro">
          <%= image_tag "qvmevent/title-ruhecanyu.png", alt: "如何参与", width: 250 -%>
        </div>

        <div class="join-bg-container">
          <div class="join-container">
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-md-2 col-sm-2 col-xs-2 col-join">
                <a href="https://portal.qiniu.com/signin" target="_blank">
                  <%= image_tag "qvmevent/join-zhuce-w.png", alt: "注册", class: "image-normal", height: "100%" -%>
                  <%= image_tag "qvmevent/join-zhuce-h.png", alt: "注册", class: "image-hover", height: "100%" -%>
                  <h4>注册</h4>
                </a>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-2 col-sm-2 col-xs-2 col-join">
                <%= image_tag "qvmevent/join-arrow.png", alt: "箭头", width: "60%" -%>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-2 col-sm-2 col-xs-2 col-join">
                <a href="https://portal.qiniu.com/identity" target="_blank">
                  <%= image_tag "qvmevent/join-renzheng-w.png", alt: "认证", class: "image-normal", height: "100%" -%>
                  <%= image_tag "qvmevent/join-renzheng-h.png", alt: "认证", class: "image-hover", height: "100%" -%>
                  <h4>认证</h4>
                </a>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-2 col-sm-2 col-xs-2 col-join">
                <%= image_tag "qvmevent/join-arrow.png", alt: "箭头", width: "60%" -%>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-2 col-sm-2 col-xs-2 col-join">
                <a href="https://portal.qiniu.com/qvm/vm/instance/create?region=cn-qingdao&activity=onermb" target="_blank">
                  <%= image_tag "qvmevent/join-goumai-w.png", alt: "购买", class: "image-normal", height: "100%" -%>
                  <%= image_tag "qvmevent/join-goumai-h.png", alt: "购买", class: "image-hover", height: "100%" -%>
                  <h4>购买</h4>
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>

    <%# rule part %>
    <div class="features features-qvm1rmb features-qvm1rmb-rule">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="intro">
          <%= image_tag "qvmevent/title-huodongguize.png", alt: "活动规则", width: 250 -%>
        </div>

        <div class="rule-bg-container">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-xs-12">

              <div class="rule-item">
                <h4>一. 活动时间</h4>
                <p>2018年9月18日 — 2018年10月17日（每天限量 50 台）</p>
              </div>

              <div class="rule-item">
                <h4>二. 活动规则</h4>
                <p>1. 本活动面向七牛云主机官网已注册且完成实名认证的企业用户</p>
                <p>2. 本活动可以 0 元价领取指定七牛云服务器机型，使用时长为 1 个月及以上（超过 1 个月自动减免首月价格）</p>
                <p>3. 本次活动区域限制在中国大陆地区</p>
                <p>4. 由于本活动为 0 元购机活动，暂不支持退款</p>
                <p>5. 为保证活动的公平公正，七牛云有权对恶意刷抢（如通过程序等技术手段）活动资源，长期资源闲置，利用资源从事违法违规行为的用户收回云资源</p>
                <p>6. 所有参加本活动的用户，均视为认可并同意遵守《七牛云用户协议》</p>
                <p>7. 活动最终解释权在法律允许范围内归七牛云所有</p>
              </div>

              <div class="rule-item">
                <h4>三. 活动支持</h4>
                <p>如您在活动或使用过程中有任何疑问，请<%= link_to "点击此处", "https://support.qiniu.com/tickets/category", class: "email-box", target: "_blank" -%>提交工单或发送邮件至 <%= link_to "marketing@qiniu.com", "mailto:marketing@qiniu.com", class:"email-box" -%></p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

</div>


